# <%= appDisplayName %>

Base React + TypeScript + Vite application generated by `t-generator`.

## Optional features

Run the feature generator from the project root:

```bash
yo t-generator:add
```

The interactive flow currently offers:

- `bff`
- `ui-library`

You can also call a feature directly when needed:

```bash
yo t-generator:add bff
yo t-generator:add ui-library
```

## UI

The preferred UI stack for this generator is based on Material UI and
`@batoanng/mui-components`. The base app stays feature-neutral until you add the
`ui-library` feature.

## Scripts

- `npm run dev`
- `npm run build`
- `npm run preview`
- `npm run lint`
- `npm run test`
